        <updateDate>2016-03-23T21:32:53Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill authorizes the governor of a state that shares a border with Canada or Mexico to designate up to 5% of its apportionment of surface transportation program funds for each fiscal year for border infrastructure projects. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
